<br>
the most common use for this is training passive skills like sence heading as an example<br>
<br>
Put your hot key for sence heading in slot 2 then look up the keyboard setup for slot 2 it will have &quot; 2 &quot; as the primary slot if you add the right or left arrow to the secondary slot every tine you turn you'll sence heading, very useful.<br>
<br>
